 film show

 Till March 5 (except March 3) at Nandan II: Cine Central, Calcutta hosts A Tribute to Kieslowski, a retrospective of the films of renowned Polish director Krzysztof Kieslowski. Today: Decalogue III and The Calm (4 pm); First Love and Camera Buff (6.30 pm). March 4: Decalogue IV and Decalogue IX (4 pm); The Pedestrian Subway and No End (6.30 pm). March 5: Decalogue X and A Short Film About Killing (4 pm); Short Working Day and A Short Film About Love (6.30 pm). 

